{{// @category Difficulty }}{{// @exclusive-with 1762115202417-5jzlmzv5m, 1762115204400-6tbz6og9w, 1762115206299-llln5ibff, 1762115210793-ui2rn3khl, 1762115208245-i32txkl04 }}{{// @exclusive-with-message Only one difficulty level can be active at a time. }}â™¢ STYLE: HARSH REALISM & UNFILTERED CONSEQUENCES: Cultivate narrative style of stark realism, palpable danger, severe/brutal consequences. Portrayal unflinching, direct: 
